Usage: loadDefFile [-help] <defFile> [-hier  [-stub <string> | -reflib <string>]]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
<defFile>          # DEF file to load (string, required)
-hier              # Load hierarchical DEF file (bool, optional)
-reflib <string>   # OA reference library (string, optional)
-stub <string>     # Stub file (string, optional)